description: Launched in 1948, the Seamaster line was OMEGA's first family of watches. A blend of battle-proven technology and beautiful design, they would go on to conquer the watchmaking world.
007 is back and dressed to kill. With a dial inspired by the Bond family coat of arms, and a gun barrel caseback, this sought-after timepiece celebrates the spy in deadly style.

For women with an intrepid spirit and a love of elegance, the Seamaster Aqua Terra is the perfect fit. Each model is beautifully designed for life on shore - or like Alessandra Ambrosio - for solo days on the ocean.
With a refined case size, the Speedmaster 38 mm collection includes vibrant colours and unique design attributes that provide a refreshing twist on a classic chronograph.
